{"tid":1590329,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警記招 正名為 真理部發佈會 Ministry of Truth Announcement","createTime":"2019-09-23T16:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T00:47:26.000Z","uid":50904,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"73b96d0a46e0aef72c167dac206a2df7b41955b8","tid":1590329,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ravZR39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FravZR39.png&h=91fe8b75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真理部（英語：Ministry of Truth），新語略作真部（Minitrue） 是英國作家喬治&middot;奧威爾所著政治諷刺小說《一九八四》中的大洋國四大政府機構之一。主角溫斯頓&middot;史密斯（Winston Smith）就在真部上班。真理部主要負責根據現實和宣傳需要，改寫歷史文獻，報紙，和文學著作。<br />\n不過，冠以真理也有深層含義，那就是人為地製造真理。<br />\n<br />\nThe Ministry of Truth (Newspeak: Minitrue) is the ministry of propaganda. As with the other ministries in the novel, the name Ministry of Truth is a misnomer because in reality it serves the opposite: it is responsible for any necessary falsification of historical events.<br />\n<br />\nAs well as administering truth, the ministry spreads a new language amongst the populace called Newspeak, in which, for example, &quot;truth&quot; is understood to mean statements like 2 + 2 = 5 when the situation warrants. In keeping with the concept of doublethink, the ministry is thus aptly named in that it creates/manufactures &quot;truth&quot; in the Newspeak sense of the word. The book describes the doctoring of historical records to show a government-approved version of events."},{"pid":"5f453f107dba82c737b13c753a6e1252e08e02ca","tid":1590329,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"75999d54a4cf19251b9eee984d1cd2d860eaadc0","tid":1590329,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:15:21.000Z","msg":"覺得連登比人滲透? 通街三毛? 全部都係打手網軍?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得個推字同正評係無用架，想反擊就入下條link嘅站務台Post，了解點樣揪出內鬼，要求連仔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>連仔必需獨立調查有組織企圖操控輿論，內含IT分析方向</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545901/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545901/</a>"},{"pid":"e28aac999c22b8c6614be9869efea64a326dca4e","tid":1590329,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:15:37.000Z","msg":"我係召集今日喺始創唱國歌嗰個小薯仔，我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590080</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c97edb47cd98212435a65c976d05544e61ddb3b6","tid":1590329,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推10連"},{"pid":"23135fcf23b82fbe9e13b388de47e63c133bb001","tid":1590329,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113342d46ea5d940305789f2ca25cb7f8c4543f2","tid":1590329,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0932e94e49aab353a5f06c393b9e89917bf6f5e","tid":1590329,"uid":50904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:17:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66007a044fc9516ced7dac0001cca1bb571e0842","tid":1590329,"uid":217807,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:18:04.000Z","msg":"1984 真係香港人必睇既一本書<img sr